        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَنْ بَرِئَ مِنَ اَللَّهِ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ صَادِقاً كَانَ أَوْ كَاذِباً فَقَدْ بَرِئَ اَللَّهُ مِنْهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4318 - Imam (as) also said: \"Whoever disassociates from Allah (swt), the Almighty and Glorious, whether truthfully or falsely, then Allah (swt) has disassociated from him.\""
        ]
